8) QA Gates (pre-promote)

âœ… Deep link refresh works on /learn, /lessons, /modules, /chat, /profile

âœ… 404 & SPA rewrite configured

âœ… Lighthouse: Perf â‰¥ 80, A11y â‰¥ 90, BP â‰¥ 90, SEO â‰¥ 90

âœ… Cross-browser: Safari, Chrome, Firefox, Edge

âœ… Slow 3G acceptable UX; offline banners & retry OK

âœ… No PII or secrets in logs or network requests

âœ… CSP & CORS verified; cookies secure flags set

âœ… Robots.txt + sitemap.xml correct for environment

âœ… Env vars point to correct API (staging vs prod)

âœ… Feature flags set to desired cohort in prod



---

9) Quick â€œDiffâ€ Checklist Before Going Live

[ ] Swap domain from staging â†’ production

[ ] Tighten CORS to prod only

[ ] Tighten CSP to prod origins

[ ] Reduce analytics sampling

[ ] Disable verbose logging

[ ] Long-TTL caching for assets enabled

[ ] Robots: allow; sitemap enabled

[ ] Source maps private (not public)

[ ] Flags set: new features OFF or small cohort

[ ] Uptime/alerting rules enabled



